<br>
I'd like to pose a question though. Those of you who want to do full random, do you random spells if someone in the group *needs* it? I was in a group last night and we got a level 60 shaman spell. The shaman in the group was given it, no roll despite the fact that it had been clearly stated that all items would be randomed. Is a spell scroll not an item? Don't get me wrong, I'm happy that the shaman got a spell scroll he didn't have yet...but it kinda seems that the randoming everything street doesn't go both ways.<br>
